snippet.title: Kujlevka — «Arrival» Trailer
snippet.description:
A flying saucer crashes in a distant Russian village, turning a run-down kolkhoz into the first thin bridge between civilizations. The outcome of this encounter and the impression we make upon the first contact depends on you!

Web: https://kujlevka.ru
Steam: shorturl.at/dxKT6
Twitter: https://twitter.com/CallbackGames
Discord: https://discord.gg/qJvuTbP

Special thanks to the band «Empty Train»!
Music: «Отражение Лиц в Окнах Вагонов»
